items.title: Awesome Yew
items.content_text:
### Projects

*   [rust-async-wasm-demo (‚≠ê50)](https://github.com/extraymond/rust-async-wasm-demo) - Toy project to learn Rust and async that can be deployed to the web.

### Crates / Component Libraries

*   [muicss-yew (‚≠ê37)](https://github.com/AlephAlpha/muicss-yew) - MUI-CSS Components for Yew framework.
*   [yew-bulma (‚≠ê21)](https://github.com/kellpossible/yew-bulma) - A Rust library providing components based on the bulma css library for projects using Yew.
*   [ybc (‚≠ê255)](https://github.com/thedodd/ybc) - A Yew component library based on the Bulma CSS framework.
*   [patternfly-yew (‚≠ê161)](https://github.com/ctron/patternfly-yew) - Patternfly components for Yew.

### Crates / Components

*   [Yew Form (‚≠ê97)](https://github.com/jfbilodeau/yew_form) - Components to simplify handling forms with Yew.

### Crates / Utils

*   [reacty\_yew (‚≠ê54)](https://github.com/hobofan/reacty_yew) - Generate Yew components from React components via Typescript type definitions.
*   [styled-yew (‚≠ê35)](https://github.com/IcyDefiance/styled-yew) - CSS in Rust, similar to styled-components, but for Yew.
